(Translated by Google) Park for both young and old. Very nice place that deserves to be better known because it is really worth it.

(Original)
Parc autant pour les petits ou les grands. Très bel endroit qui mérite d'être plus connu car il vaut vraiment la peine.

(Translated by Google) Very nice park

(Original)
Tres beau parc
